tle from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Volume 22, Number 19 (July 19, 1945) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:57.206Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271256/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["red lodge", "carbon", "united states", "montana"], "number": ["online resource", "2020271256", "1225296162", "2766-1326", "2020271257", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "carbon county news (red lodge, carbon county, montana) 1936-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 48.689003, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "carbon", "montana", "red lodge", "united states", "red lodge (mont.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:07.415Z", "title": "Carbon County news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271256/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271257/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1931", "dates": ["[1931 TO 1936]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. VIII, no. 32 (October 15, 1931); ceased with vol. XIII, no. 9 (May 1, 1936). \"Republican.\" Cf. Directory of Montana newspapers, 1935-1936. \"Official paper of Carbon County and the City of Red Lodge.\" Carries also numbering for Red Lodge daily news (non-extant). Vol. VIII, No. 32 (October 15, 1931); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Vol. XIII, No. 9 (May 1, 1936) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Carbon County news (Red Lodge, Mont. : 1936) 2766-1326 (DLC) 2020271256 (OCoLC)1225296162"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:57.206Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271257/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["red lodge", "carbon", "united states", "montana"], "number": ["online resource", "1225373628", "2020271258", "2766-1350", "2020271256", "2020271257", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "red lodge daily news combined with carbon county news (red lodge, carbon county, montana) 1931-1936 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 48.689003, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "carbon", "montana", "red lodge", "united states", "red lodge (mont.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:07.415Z", "title": "Red Lodge daily news combined with Carbon County news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271257/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271258/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1924", "dates": ["[1924 TO 1931]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. 1, no. 33 (November 6, 1924); ceased with vol. VIII, no. 31 (October 3, 1931). \"Republican.\" Cf. Directory of Montana newspapers, 1925-1931. \"Official paper of the City of Red Lodge,\" 1926-1931; \"official paper of Carbon County,\" 1927-1931. Vol. 1, No. 33 (November 6, 1924); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Vol. VIII, no. 31 (October 3, 1931) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Red Lodge daily news combined with Carbon County news 2766-1350 (DLC) 2020271257 (OCoLC)1225373628"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:57.206Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271258/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["red lodge", "carbon", "united states", "montana"], "number": ["online resource", "1225499348", "2766-1377", "2020271258", "2020271259", "2020271257", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the carbon county news (red lodge, carbon county, montana) 1924-1931 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 48.689003, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "carbon", "montana", "red lodge", "united states", "red lodge (mont.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:07.415Z", "title": "The Carbon County news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271258/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271259/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1924", "dates": ["[1924 TO 1924]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with volume 1, number 1 (March 21, 1924); ceased with vol. 1, no. 32 (October 29, 1924). \"Politically the Chronicle will be a Republican newspaper.\" Volume 1, Number 2 (March 28, 1924); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Vol. 1, No. 32 (October 29, 1924) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 4, 2020). Carbon County news (Red Lodge, Mont. : 1924) 2766-1377 (DLC) 2020271258 (OCoLC)1225499348"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:57.206Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271259/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["red lodge", "carbon", "united states", "montana"], "number": ["online resource", "1225499542", "2766-1393", "2020271258", "2020271259", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the carbon county chronicle (red lodge, carbon county, montana) 1924-1924 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 48.689003, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "carbon", "montana", "red lodge", "united states", "red lodge (mont.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:07.415Z", "title": "The Carbon County chronicle", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271259/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2014218352/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1889", "dates": ["[1889 TO 1907]"], "description": ["Weekly Began September 1, 1889; ceased October 11, 1907. \"The Picket will be found in the ranks of Republican newspapers.\" \"Official newspaper of Carbon County,\" 1896/1897, 1898-1907; \"official newspaper of ... the City of Red Lodge, \" 1900-1907. Published every Saturday from December 21, 1889 through August 13, 1899. Published every Friday starting January 5, 1900. Publisher: The Picket Publishing Company, <January 3-December 26, 1902>. Description based on: Vol. 1, no. 16 (December 21, 1889); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 7, 2014). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XIV, no. 25 (December 26, 1902) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 7, 2014). Carbon County Republican (Online) Republican picket (Online)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:25.703Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2014218352/", "image_url": [], "index": 9, "language": ["english"], "location": ["red lodge", "carbon", "united states", "montana"], "number": ["online resource", "2372-8809", "2014218352", "879336062", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["red lodge picket (red lodge, park county, montana) 1889-1907 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 48.689003, "shel